Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.93,0:00:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...l met Chihiro, my first sweetheart, and started a long-distance relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.10,0:00:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l had a chance to date another girl unexpectedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.31,0:00:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l ended up having sex with her, but l was really just a victim of circumstance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.91,0:00:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was regretting what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.48,0:00:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, l walked past Chihiro while l was on a date with the girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.82,0:00:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and l didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.09,0:00:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l absolutely don't want to break up with Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.29,0:00:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was willing to accept any blame to get her back, so l chased her...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.46,0:00:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...only to find that she was on a date with a strange man.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.92,0:00:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know l screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.75,0:01:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she also cheated on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.86,0:01:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikuson...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.03,0:01:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikuson...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.60,0:01:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikuson...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikuson...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.04,0:01:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.77,0:01:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you looking for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My dog is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.54,0:01:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.62,0:01:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikuson, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.72,0:01:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikuson!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.35,0:01:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.22,0:01:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might not be here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.96,0:01:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikuson.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.79,0:01:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.23,0:01:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikuson!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.03,0:01:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.20,0:01:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikuson, come out from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.97,0:01:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, you should listen to your mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.11,0:01:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.79,0:02:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikuson!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.36,0:02:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro, been waiting long?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.13,0:02:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.83,0:02:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l haven't seen you for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.27,0:02:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head over heels in love?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can l have a tea with milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.51,0:02:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's about Fukuroi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bumped into a high school friend, who had moved away...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.58,0:02:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the two of you fell in love with each other, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dramatic!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.25,0:02:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.32,0:02:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's so lucky that we are close to my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.06,0:02:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You would catch a cold if you went back home with wet clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,0:02:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one else is home, so you can take a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.87,0:02:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.97,0:02:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are such a troublesome dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mistress got drenched to the skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miku-chan is her name...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's cute, but she still seems immature.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.00,0:03:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.24,0:03:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She may act young, but her body is sure mature enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l finished taking a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't leave my relationship with Fukuroi-kun vague.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l should talk to him and make it clear...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls this Fukuroi-san residence?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.06,0:04:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.23,0:04:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, only Masato is here right now and he's taking a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was just in this bath a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My love affair with Chihiro is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares if l make love to other girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since then, Miku and l often met.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.43,0:05:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We both love reading, and we can talk for hours and hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we are just friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We get along, but we don't have any special feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Chihiro-chan isn't the only woman out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be disappointed and good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l won't be able to attend this party, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:05:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about Chieri-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l broke up with Chieri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.49,0:06:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't get along with that sex animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l heard about your breakup, but l didn't know she was a sex fiend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.07,0:06:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls she perverted?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.18,0:06:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just into the normal stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but she's like a cat in heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work together here on Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.09,0:06:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get an extra 50% per an hour 'cause it's overtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After l met Miku, l started working on my unfinished novel again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But actually l am wondering how much...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...of what l put into the novel is the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because the story is about Chihiro and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.21,0:06:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuroi-san will be a novelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:06:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know if l really will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You definitely will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.49,0:07:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only books and Hikuson used to be my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so l hope my new friend, Fukuroi-san, has his dreams come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miku...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me read it after you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls it difficult to write a novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.35,0:07:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wonder if l can write.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.42,0:07:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.35,0:07:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of story you want to write?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.88,0:07:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a love story.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm looking forward to reading your love story.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, l can't do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've never been kissed, and l've never had sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, l can't write a love story.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't write such a thing without experience, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l-l have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.88,0:08:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want to write a love story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuroi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My love affair of Chihiro is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can do anything l want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.64,0:08:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miku wants me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.13,0:09:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, l want to write my own love story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, not there...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.85,0:09:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall l stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touch this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, move slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.12,0:09:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move faster gradually.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, make more noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:09:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.84,0:10:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep sucking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may feel a little pain, but you'll have to get over it for sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you turned on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feels good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.27,0:10:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miku, this is sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.61,0:10:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So good, l feel like l'm melting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, l'm climbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l feel so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such an innocent girl opens her heart for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She may not be able to do anything without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, l'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.18,0:11:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miku, l'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come inside me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.59,0:11:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...has something been wrong recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.83,0:11:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l felt something different when l met you last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's strange that you always hang out with me, who doesn't have a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.73,0:11:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you haven't been getting along well with Fukuroi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, we don't see each other much, because we live far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:12:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, we talk on the phone everyday...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.02,0:12:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro isn't telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, l'm sure the cause of all this is Fukuroi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a friend, l can't ignore it any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.90,0:12:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You used to be Masato's classmate in high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.77,0:12:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He skipped work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't show up because he has a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.05,0:12:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're his former classmate, that means you are a friend of Chihiro, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.99,0:12:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like they broke up with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masato is stupid to break up with Chihiro-chan, she's a great girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't get a girl like her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.57,0:12:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro and Fukuroi-kun broke up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:13:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you know what's going on, could you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, but here is not appropriate...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll finish my shift soon, so after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you let me know about Fukuroi-kun before doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.83,0:13:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have a terrible memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l am trying to bring the details to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what's with all the noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're dripping everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you came here for an important errand, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall l stop in the middle?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oka-kun, have you remembered anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, if you rush me too much, you'll make it harder for me to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:14:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Masato and Chihiro-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've become very forgetful, haven't l?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Masato, how's your cold doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l heard from Oka-kun about what's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuroi-kun, you've really misunderstood Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misunderstood?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l saw Chihiro kiss somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That gave you a big shock, l guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l haven't heard that Chihiro has a new boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you did see her kiss a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...l guess she was a victim of circumstance...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or there was some good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.75,0:14:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l agree, a kiss could happen under some circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's just a kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l will ask Chihiro about the kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll persuade her to do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...like apologize or explain it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if Chihiro apologizes to you, please think about her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.84,0:15:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro hasn't said anything to me, but l know she still likes you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good news, right Masato?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.32,0:15:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't start to hate her, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a good chance to see her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy probably wasn't her boyfriend, and it was just a kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.19,0:15:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you compare that to when l made love with Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miku...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.27,0:15:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming, but l have friends visiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't send them away...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l see, you have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.02,0:15:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vitamin C is good for a cold, l heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:15:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, strawberries, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please get well soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you are not well, l'm not well, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, l'll recover soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuroi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.97,0:16:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miku appeared, but l hadn't even introduced her to my friend, Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.51,0:16:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna, who was trying to mediate between Chihiro and me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was pretty shocked to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.95,0:16:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After everything, l lost my chance to go back to Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they go home because l came by and they took the hint?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.54,0:16:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.77,0:16:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuroi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.31,0:16:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you do me a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.94,0:16:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.25,0:17:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you come with me to the Christmas party at Marine Palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.28,0:17:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.65,0:17:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll catch my cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.62,0:17:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't mind, as long as the cold is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You went all the way to Namikaze City for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.58,0:17:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l am fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.79,0:17:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l assumed that Fukuroi-kun and l had already broken up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.52,0:17:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, l need to find a restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuroi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been seeing another girl, like l thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have no idea what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miku started to write a novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She used to be shy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but since she started writing, that's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.43,0:18:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she'll probably complete her novel before...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...l finish mine, because l'm so lazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lshimaru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro-chan, do you have any plans for Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm really impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You story is so well organized, even though this is your first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l feel your character's passion first and foremost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, l'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.60,0:18:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll read once more later and give you detailed comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please take care of me, my teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop calling me a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.17,0:19:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh teacher, please let me read your novel soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not finished yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.05,0:19:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's taking so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're suffering from writer's block?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.82,0:19:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l-lt's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf not, why don't you let me read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's okay, even if it's not finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.79,0:19:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be looking forward to reading it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have to go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without completing the novel, it seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that my relationship with Chihiro is not really over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, l am being impolite to Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.15,0:19:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have to take care of her, she'll probably be relying on me from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:19:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuroi-san, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls this mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.27,0:20:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l took it and brought it home...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because l was dying to read your novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After finishing, l wanted you to read it first, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuroi-san, this story is based on real life, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, some of it is based on real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuroi-san, you still love her, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l hope you win back that love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.07,0:20:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Win back love?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm going out with Miku right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.04,0:20:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, l'm not the person you are in love with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You love the girl from this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuroi-san, you taught me how to write.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.85,0:21:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have confidence in myself for the first time in my life because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, l want to return your kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.23,0:21:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want to do something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miku, you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.57,0:21:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.24,0:21:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have confidence in myself, but l'm sad because you are leaving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf l write novels and express myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.15,0:21:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...l'll have a positive outlook on life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.12,0:21:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought that Miku was immature, but she has become independent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was mortified, she pointed out my true intentions...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...which l had not realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.56,0:21:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuroi-san, go see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll go see Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:21:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.72,0:22:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't care what happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.49,0:22:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll go or l'll regret it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.09,0:22:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.19,0:22:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt doesn't always go like a novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.73,0:22:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.13,0:22:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's too late to...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.50,0:22:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...win back her love now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.37,0:22:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's absolutely unrealistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.36,0:23:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.56,0:23:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuroi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.13,0:23:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro, why you are here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.53,0:23:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so silly...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.56,0:23:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l went to your place, and then l heard you went my place...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.84,0:23:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so l hoped you'd appear here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.94,0:23:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.41,0:23:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.61,0:23:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l decided you were wrong for me without being sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.32,0:23:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgetting about what l did, l blamed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.62,0:23:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro, why don't we go out again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.69,0:23:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.73,0:24:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.06,0:24:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.31,0:24:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro, l love you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.14,0:25:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuroi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.41,0:25:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here l come.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.24,0:26:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so good...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.62,0:26:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.63,0:26:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.44,0:26:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.75,0:27:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l-l'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.95,0:27:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second chapter of our relationship started like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.79,0:27:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, l've figured out how to develop the story l've always wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.90,0:27:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Chihiro, for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.27,0:27:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuroi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.64,0:27:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.64,0:27:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss me, please.
